{"article_id":"AtqQ3WqYwUAQ4tDd","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Donald Trump has agreed to a Democratic plan","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"to lift the debt limit for three months ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"fund the government","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"and rush aid to Hurricane Harvey victims .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"The US president went against Republican leaders","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"who wanted to extend a debt-limit increase for longer , until after the 2018 mid-term elections .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Democrats announced the deal","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"just before the House of Representatives passed $ 8bn","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"( £6bn )","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"for Harvey victims .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Congress will need to approve the deal","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"before it is finalised .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"Mr Trump told reporters aboard Air Force One","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"he had a `` very good meeting '' with House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi and Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"`` We essentially came to a deal","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"and I think","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"the deal will be very good , ''","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"he said","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"while travelling to North Dakota for an event on tax reform on Wednesday .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"`` We agreed to a three-month extension on debt ceiling ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"which they consider to be sacred , very important . ''","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"The proposal attaches the disaster aid to a government funding bill","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that would raise the US debt limit","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"and keep the government running through 15 December ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"setting up a fiscal showdown at the end of the year","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that Republicans had hoped to avoid .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"`` Both sides have every intention","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"of avoiding default in December","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"and look forward to working together on the many issues before us , ''","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Mrs Pelosi and Mr Schumer said in a joint statement .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Leaders from both parties met Mr Trump at the White House on Wednesday morning .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Following the meeting ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Republican House Speaker Paul Ryan called the Democratic proposal `` unworkable '' and `` ridiculous '' ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"putting the president at odds with his own party .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"`` Meet the swamp :","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Trump sides with Democrats during leadership confab '' ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"comments Breitbart on the front page of its website ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"by doing so","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"he `` jacks up debt ,","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"punts the agenda ,","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"snubs GOP '' .","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"`` This is n't Trump caving in to the Democrats .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"No no no .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"This is Trump sticking it to the Establishment , you guys .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"That 's all , ''","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"comments Joe Cunningham of RedState .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"`` President Trump waged a hostile takeover of the Republican Party 's presidential nomination last year .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Now he 's holding the entire party hostage , ''","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"says an editorial in The Washington Post .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"`` The bargain has left several Republican lawmakers seething","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"that Trump , the self-proclaimed deal-maker , had given such leverage to their political rivals , ''","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"The Los Angeles Times reports .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"It says","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that the president has grown increasingly frustrated over dissent in his party","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"which","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"he believes","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"has stifled his agenda .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"`` [ If Mr Trump 's ] deal did not yet represent the breaking point between the president and his core , hard-right base of support ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"it certainly put him closer","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"than he has ever been","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"to tipping his fragile political coalition into open revolt , ''","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"New York Times columnists Jeremy W Peters and Maggie Habierman write .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Treasury Secretary Steve Mnuchin had also reportedly urged Mr Trump to pursue a longer-term debt-limit deal","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"but has insisted","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"that raising the borrowing limit was imperative","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"in order to quickly send aid to Texas .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"The deal includes Democratic support in the Senate for the first instalment of disaster relief aid for Hurricane Harvey victims in Houston ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"where flooding has devastated the Texan city .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Texas Governor Greg Abbott has warned","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"the cost of reconstruction","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"after Hurricane Harvey","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"could be as high as $ 180bn .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"The House overwhelmingly passed a bill","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"to provide $ 7.9bn for victims of the floods","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"before the Federal Emergency Management Agency","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"( Fema )","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"runs out of funds later this week .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"The House approved the funding 419 to three ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"with three Republicans voting `` no '' .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Democrats on the House floor pointed out","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"that Republicans refused to pass a $ 50.5bn disaster relief package in the aftermath of the 2012 Superstorm Sandy ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"which ravaged north-east states ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"because it was not offset by budget savings elsewhere .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"The north-east states","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"that were hit hardest by Sandy","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"are predominantly Democratic","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"while Texas and much of the southern US leans Republican .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"The relief package comes","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"as a more powerful storm , Hurricane Irma , barrels toward Puerto Rico and Florida","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"and threatens more damage .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Mr Trump 's deal with the Democrats means","depth":3},{"id":93,"text":"that the Republican-controlled Congress will have to address partisan issues such as healthcare and immigration later in the year","depth":4},{"id":94,"text":"while negotiating with Democrats over a debt vote .","depth":4},{"id":95,"text":"`` Given Republican difficulty","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"in finding the votes for their plan ,","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"we believe","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"this proposal offers a bipartisan path forward","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"to ensure prompt delivery of Harvey aid","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"as well as avoiding a default ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"while both sides work together","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"to address government funding , DREAMERS , and healthcare , ''","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"Mr Schumer and Mrs Pelosi said .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":207,"left":195,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":115,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":109,"right":114,"relat